---
import Header from "../components/Header";
import SocialMediaFooter from "../components/SocialMediaFooter";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />
  <main class="w-1/2 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="mt-32 mb-20 text-center">About</h1>
    <section class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b-2 p-10 bg-secondary text-primary rounded-xl">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold py-5">Joshua Borseth</h2>
        <ul class="text-xl list-disc font-bold ml-5">
          <li>React Lover</li>
          <li>Typescript Enthusiast</li>
          <li>Tailwind Fan Boy</li>
          <li>Vercel Fanatic</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-evenly items-center rounded p-2">
        <img
          src="/bitmoji.png"
          alt="Bitmoji avatar icon."
          class="border-4 border-primary rounded-full"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>How I Found Web Dev</h2>
      <p>
        After a year of the Computer Information Systems Program at UFV, I knew I had found my
        passion. Web Development. It started out as just a hobby as UFV taught me a lot more about
        hardware than they did software. During this year I focused a lot of my attention on my
        foundational programming skills by myself. This is why I consider myself to be a Self Taught
        Web Developer.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <SocialMediaFooter client:load />
</Layout>
